Company Description: Mcdonald S Is One Of The Leading Global Food Service Retailers With More Than 30,000 Local Restaurants That Serve Over 50 Million People IN Approximately 100 Countries Each Day. It Sells Hamburgers, Chicken, French Fries, Breakfasts, Salads, Fruit, Snack Wraps And Carrot Sticks. The Restaurant S Menu Features A Variety Of Burgers, Such As The Big Mac And Quarter Pounder, As Well As Chicken Mcnuggets And Egg Mcmuffins. Mcdonald S Also Offers An Array Of Beverages, Such As Soda, Ice Tea, Orange Juice, Milk And Coffee. It Also Features Interactive Game Zones That Are Designed For Children And Are Equipped With Stationary Bicycles Attached To Video Games, Basketball Hoops, Monkey Bars And Obstacle Courses. Mcdonald S Maintains A Location IN Staten Island, N.Y.

The Restaurant Chain Serves Various Food Items, Including Fries, Burgers, Chicken Nuggets, Salads, Wraps, Sandwiches As Well As Other Side Dishes. The Chain Also Provides Meal Bundles, Including The Dollar Menu, Extra Value Meals, Happy Meals And Mighty Kids Meals For Families And Children.
